==English==
===Etymology===
''[[snow]]'' + ''[[man]]'' 

===Noun===

{{en-noun|snowmen}}

# A humanoid figure made with large [[snowball]]s stacked on each other. Human traits like a face and arms are fashioned with sticks (arms), a carrot (nose), and stones or coal (eyes, mouth).

